{
  "text": "Testosterone \" Testosterone was determined in serum using an ECLIA (Roche Diagnostics GmbH) as described [CITATION_1] . Intra-and inter-assay CV were 2.4 and 2.6% for a mean testosterone concentration of 176 ng/dl (6.10 nmol/l), and 1.2 and 2.3% for a mean testosterone concentration of 455 ng/dl (15.78 nmol/l) respectively.",
